title: #59a: Fat (Ralphie May)
itunes:title: Fat with Ralphie May - Part 1
description: Ralphie May bought me breakfast and took me up to his house to talk to me about what it's like to be a fat guy. Interesting conversation. I split it up into 2 parts because it went so long. There's still a good hour plus left.
